7 An Act relating to children; directing the Department
of Human Services to work with the State Fire Marshal
8 to develop certain guidelines; declaring certain
child care homes shall not be denied license if
9 complies with the IRC; prohibiting stricter
requirements than those outlined in the IRC;
10 providing for codification; and providing an
